reviewText: I knew ahead of time that his recipes are kinda "pedestrian" for a gourmet. I believe that a true gourmet would see this as " how to make good tasting stuff quick and easy". He is a fun watch and would be a great push to get people who think that they cannot cook to give it a try.
Simple easy to follow. Cooks everything from start to finish in front of you, no prep guys. Go to YouTube if you want to see a sample of his work. Great for teaching teens how to cook.
